data_table.description: Sample ID, ESP phenotype, body site where sample was obtained, analyte type, and tumor status of subjects participated in the "National Heart Lung and Blood Institute (NHLBI) GO-ESP: Heart Cohorts Component of the Exome Sequencing Project (JHS)" sub study of the "Jackson Heart Study (JHS) Cohort" project.

variable.name: SAMPID
variable.description: Sample ID [for individual vcf files from sequencing sites]

variable.name: ESP_phenotype
variable.description: ESP Phenotype group [phenotype that the sample was selected to be sequenced for] [EOMI_Control (Early MI control); LDL_Low; LDL_High; BP_Low (low blood pressure); BP_High (high blood pressure); DPR (Deeply phenotyped reference); BMI_High]

variable.name: Body_site
variable.description: Body site or tissue that sample is from [Blood]

variable.name: Is_tumor
variable.description: Indicator of whether sample from tumor [N=No]
